Hartman, 1955: 41; 
<bibRefCitation author="Fauchald, K" journalOrPublisher="Natural History Museum of Los Angeles County, Science Series" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" pagination="1 - 188" title="The polychaete worms. Definitions and keys to the orders, families and genera." url="http://www.vliz.be/imisdocs/publications/123110.pdf" volume="28" year="1977">Fauchald 1977</bibRefCitation>
